{"tid":1631583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟仲係咪要人擔遮遮勇武？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:53.000Z","uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03bda1253ca1981f9236f13f51b9dcf23660a289","tid":1631583,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"擔遮嘅人我明白你地好想對件事有貢獻 有做到嘢<br />\n首先我好多謝你地<br />\n<br />\n但場運動到咗宜家呢個階段 大家都知道勇武會打咩牌 係咪仲有擔遮嘅需要？<br />\n好多時狗仔衝過嚟或者射幾粒煙過嚟就會中咗好多擔遮嘅人 而且好多擔遮嘅人都唔係full gear<br />\n但因為佢地企嘅位置就係最前線 要承受嘅攻擊係因前線無異 <br />\n咁呢個時候 擔遮嘅人就會大大降低活動能力<br />\n係咁狗仔一衝就會捉到好多擔遮嘅人<br />\n咁武勇係走好定救好？<br />\n相信大家睇咁多片都知道勇武都係有良心嘅人<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想話任何一個人係拖緊人後腿<br />\n每一個人嘅任何付出 都係功不可沒<br />\n只係宜家個玩法唔同咗 我地係咪都要與時並進呢？"},{"pid":"c2327aace5739288ff7761a8e134edb7b44c9fe9","tid":1631583,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔係為左遮樣咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個腦去左邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58fd7d3338617cb79d07958833fd6948b9196cd","tid":1631583,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"784c7450e7ef7d629f0400d107cc33980ad20b40","tid":1631583,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2327aace5739288ff7761a8e134edb7b44c9fe9","tid":1631583,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔係為左遮樣咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個腦去左邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"你見到前線有勇武係打大個樣出嚟嘅咩？<br />\n你對眼去咗邊"},{"pid":"432454a6cb4818ba74d521c26212ca0bdcda7bff","tid":1631583,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"Pull"},{"pid":"743474f0575ad9c8663b9b127786469412e18f16","tid":1631583,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784c7450e7ef7d629f0400d107cc33980ad20b40","tid":1631583,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2327aace5739288ff7761a8e134edb7b44c9fe9","tid":1631583,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔係為左遮樣咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個腦去左邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"你見到前線有勇武係打大個樣出嚟嘅咩？<br />\n你對眼去咗邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"你真係幾好笑 衣著 某種五官特徵 大撚把可以trace<br />\n遮住做 散開 比你跟到人又點？你證實到係邊個做？<br />\n用下個閪腦啦"}]}